        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "## Lecture21\n- **Flow:** `POST /orders` (once) → **`POST /orders/:id/request-payment` ×80** on the same order.\n- **Metrics:** Nest exposes **`GET /metrics`** (`prom-client` histogram `http_request_duration_seconds`). Route label is normalized, e.g. `POST /orders/:id/request-payment`.\n- **Stack:** Prometheus scrapes `host.docker.internal:3000` every 5s; Grafana datasource UID `prometheus-ds`.\n\nGenerate load (your script or `fetch`), keep this tab open ~1–2 minutes so `rate()` has data, then screenshot.",
